<div class="tp-caption Fashion-BigDisplay   tp-resizeme  quote" id="slide-6-layer-1" data-x="['center','center','center','center']" data-hoffset="['0','0','0','0']" data-y="['middle','middle','middle','middle']" data-voffset="['-48','-48','-48','-48']" data-width="['1042','1042','671','671']" data-height="['none','none','109','109']" data-whitespace="normal" data-transform_idle="o:1;" data-transform_in="opacity:0;s:300;e:Power2.easeInOut;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:300;s:300;" data-start="500" data-splitin="none" data-splitout="none" data-responsive_offset="on" style="z-index: 5; min-width: 1042px; max-width: 1042px; white-space: normal; font-size: 34px; line-height: 36px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1.00);text-align:center;">“We welcome any country where the people own the Government, and not the Government the people.”
</div>

<div class="tp-caption Fashion-BigDisplay   tp-resizeme  quote-name" id="slide-6-layer-2" data-x="['center','center','center','center']" data-hoffset="['0','0','0','0']" data-y="['top','top','top','top']" data-voffset="['229','229','592','592']" data-width="594" data-height="61" data-whitespace="normal" data-transform_idle="o:1;" data-transform_in="opacity:0;s:300;e:Power2.easeInOut;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:300;s:300;" data-start="500" data-splitin="none" data-splitout="none" data-responsive_offset="on" style="z-index: 6; min-width: 594px; max-width: 594px; max-width: 61px; max-width: 61px; white-space: normal; font-size: 24px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1.00);text-align:center;">—The Hague, Netherlands, 7 May 1948
</div>
</li>

